http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/15july96/rusty.html 204.71.237.85 19970114073650 text/html 5321
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 07:37:11 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 02-Jul-96 19:58:40 GMT
