http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/22apr96/rusty.html 204.71.237.85 19970114074607 text/html 4907
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 07:46:29 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 09-Apr-96 19:36:18 GMT
