<P>09:05 UNIDENTIFIED MALE: Good morning, Mr. Vice President.
<P>VPOTUS: Good morning, Dick.
<P>UN.MALE: I have good news, Mr. Vice President. Steve Forbes is pulling out of the race.
<P>VPOTUS: That is good news. All along I've said that he was only Republican who could beat us. Dynamic speaker. Good with the crowds.
<P>UN.MALE: Yes, well. The point is, sir, that that leaves Bob Dole the Republican nominee. We'd like to start getting out the big guns. And we were wondering -- 
