http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/31dec95/rusty.htm 204.71.237.85 19970114075951 text/html 4604
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:00:13 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 27-Dec-95 15:56:22 GMT
Content-length: 4417
Content-type: text/html
