http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/11dec95/week.htm 204.71.237.85 19970114080312 text/html 12074
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:03:31 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:49 GMT
