http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/14aug95/cigar.htm 204.71.237.85 19970114081643 text/html 7576
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:17:03 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:45 GMT
