http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/21july95/week.htm 204.71.237.85 19970114082007 text/html 11556
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:20:30 GMT
