<DOCHDR>
http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/daily/nr112796.html 204.71.237.85 19970114083134 text/html 3154
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:31:53 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 02-Dec-96 23:55:41 GMT
Content-length: 2970
