<DOCOLDNO>IA029-000317-B004-460</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://nationalreview.com:80/nationalreview/extra/010897x.html 204.71.237.85 19970114083707 text/html 2602
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:37:23 GMT
