<TITLE>Senior-Inet Home Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->

<font size=4><B>Welcome to</b><BR>
 <img border=0 width=350 height=75
SRC="./graphics/sifnlog2.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
<b> or more fully</b>
<font size=3>

<HR SIZE=2>
<center>
<h1>
The Senior Information Network
</h1>
</B><font size=3>
</center>
Welcome to the Senior Information Network. The premier high tech source in obtaining information about Senior Support Services across the United States. This is made possible in two ways:
<BR>
<BR>
<ul>
<li>
  For various information categories such as Housing, Rehabilitation, Banking,
etc. interesting articles will be selected to keep one up-to-date with senior information and issues.<BR>
<BR>
<li>
 Specific information can be obtained via Web Pages by selected cities. For example: If someone from Boston, MA wishes to find out about Independent Living Housing in Colorado Springs, CO, they will start with this Home Page, be able to select
Housing, then either select articles concerning  Housing, or go directly to Web Sites for Independent Housing facilities in Colorado Springs.
</ul>     
<P>
<P>So get started by selecting a category like Housing and keep coming back as we continue to fill in this network.<p>
Please register with the Senior Information Network by completing this <A HREF="guest.htm">form</A> for the <A HREF="guest.htm">Senior Information Network.</A> 
<p> 
<p>The Senior Information Network is best viewed with a web browser that supports HTML
version 2 syntax (i.e. Netscape, Prodigy, Microsoft Network, etc). For more <A HREF="browser.htm">Web Browser</a> information, click <A HREF="browser.htm">here</A>.
<BR>
<BR>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash5.gif"><BR>
</center>
<!-- The following is the list of options to select from    -->

<h3>
<B>Senior Topics:</B>
</h3>
<ul>
<LI>
<A HREF="assocpg.htm">Association Directory</A>
--<i>senior resource associations</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="bankpg.htm">Banking</A>
--<i>with an emphasis on Senior Services</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="daycarpg.htm">Day Care Services</A>
--<i>professional senior day care services</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="hlthpg.htm">Health Care</A>
--<i>from Hospitals to Clinics to Personal Care</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="homecrpg.htm">Home Care</A>
--<i>a broad spectrum of in-home care</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="houspg.htm">Housing</A>
--<i>from independent living to long term care</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="finplpg.htm">Financial Planning</A>
--<i>financial planning-insurance, mutual funds, etc</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="insurepg.htm">Insurance</A>
--<i>from Annuities to Long term care to supplemental</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="rehabpg.htm">Rehabilitation</A>
--<i>rehabilitation services for seniors</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="socsecpg.htm">Social Security</A>
--<i>rules, regulations and discussions</i><BR>
<p>
<LI>
<A HREF="travpg.htm">Travel</A>
--<i>from places to agencies</i><BR>
<p>
</ul>
<P>
If you would like to find out about something that isn't listed yet, or would like information on web pages,  please contact us at 
 <IMG SRC="./graphics/mail.gif"> <A HREF="mailto:smingus@rmii.com">Senior Information Network.</A>
<BR>
