<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Senior Day Care Service Directory</TITLE>
<img border=0 width=350 height=50
SRC="./graphics/sifnlogo.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM"><BR>
<HR SIZE=4>
<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->
<center>
<H1>Senior Day Care Service Directory</H1>
</center>

<BR>
Adult Day Care Services are a very specialized field of senior services that has developed only recently.  The need for such services, however, has been around for a long time<p>
The mission of Adult Day Care Centers is to help caregivers to provide respite for their efforts in caring for an elderly person, usually a parent.<p>
This is generally accomplished by professionals who can provide services like medication monitoring and specialized activities during daytime hours to allow the caregiver time for work or just some time alone.
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR><BR>
</center>
This page is designed to allow you to view, read and print articles specifically related to Senior Day Care Services, and to allow you to browse your way to Senior Day Care via a City Page, and then individual web pages for Senior Day Care Service Facilities.
<p>
Select your city for Senior Day Care Services from below...:<p>
<A HREF="./cospdayc.htm">Colorado Springs, CO,  
<A HREF="./pubdayc.htm">Pueblo, CO<p> 
<BR> 
