<center>
<H1>Senior Health Care Directory</H1>
</center>

<BR>

Obviously, Senior Health Care encompasses a wide range of services. So within this 
series of web pages we will attempt to categorize as conveniently as possible.
<P>
<P>One thing to remember is that seniors bring with them a health history. So this 
usually means that the health care service that listens best will provide the best service to the needs of the senior citizen.
<BR>
<BR>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>

<P>This page is designed to allow you to view, read and print articles specifically related 
to Senior Health Care; and to allow you to browse your way to Senior Health Care via a 
City Page, and then individual Web Pages for Senior Health Care Facilities.
