<center>
<H1>Senior Financial Planning Directory</H1>
</center>

<BR>

Senior Financial Planning encompasses a number of things: insurance programs. mutual funds, 401K and other IRA plans, living trusts, reverse mortgages, etc.  
<P>
<P>This is one of those areas that needs plenty of pre-planning, and then plenty of reevaluation. And, it's not usually a do-it-yourself project! Fortunately, there is plenty of good help available.
<P>
<P>But, we will add here, look before you leap. There are also guys out there who have targeted seniors as easy. Any questions? Call the local Better Business Bureau before you hand over your hard-earned savings.
<BR>
<BR>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>

<P>This page is designed to allow you to view, read and print articles specifically related 
to Senior Financial Planning; and to allow you to browse your way to Senior Financial Planning via a City Page, and then individual Web Pages for Senior Financial Planning Providers.
<h4>
<B>Senior Financial Planning Articles:</B>
</h4>
<ul>
<LI>
