<center>
<H1>Insurance Directory</H1>
</center>
Insurance for seniors can cover a whole range and combination of topics, so we've decided to make <i>Senior Insurance</i> a category of itself even though insurance planning and financial planning go hand-in hand. Senior Insurance would include such areas as Medicaid, Supplemental (Medigap) Insurance, Annuities and Long Term Care Insurance.<p>
There are a lot of people who would like to talk to you about insurance, so be careful and do a lot of listening for second opinions before signing your name and writing your check.
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>
<P>This page is designed to allow you to view, read, and print articles specifically related to Senior Insurance; and to allow you to browse your way to Senior Insurance via a City Page, and then to individual Web Pages for Senior Insurance Providers.
<h4> 
<B>Senior Insurance articles:</B><p>
<ul>
<LI>
<A HREF="./articles/ins1.htm">Home Medical Devices</A></b>
--<i>may be a draw for scam artists</i><img width=28 height=11 alt=" [new]" src="./graphics/new2.gif">
<p>
</ul>
<P>
