<center>
<H1>Senior Rehabilitation Directory</H1>
</center>
Senior Rehabilitation starts with the basic programs of Physical Therapy, Occupational Therapy and Speech Therapy. But actually there are many variations of specialties within these general headings. For example: Head Injury Care is a special subject, Wound Care is a specialized field, etc.
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>
<P>This page is designed to get you started towards the individual web pages where each rehabilitation organization or facility can outline how it best fits into your need program. From here you can read or print articles concerned with rehabilitation and/or go explore rehabilitation resources by city.
<h4>
<B>Senior Rehabilitation Articles:</B>
</h4>
<ul>
<LI>
<A HREF="./articles/rehab1.htm">Occupational therapy</A>
--<i>improving safety and independence</i><BR>
</ul>
