<H1>Social Security Directory</H1>
</center>

<BR>

This page is formatted differently than others in the Senior Information Network. We receive a lot of good information from Social Security and thought that no senior resource network would be complete without presenting articles on this subject. So feel free to browse and down load those of interest, but you'll note that there wont be any web pages for suppliers of Social Security in each community, obviously. Further help can be obtained from your local Social Security office, or by dialing 1-800-772-1213. (Be patient, though!) 
<P>
