<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->
<center>
<H1>BANKING PAGE</H1>
<H3>Denver,  Colorado</H3>
<img border=0 width=175 height=180
<IMG SRC="./graphics/dencop1.jpg" ALT="[picture]" ALIGN=center><BR>
<BR>
</center>
Denver Colorado, the mile high city, is the state capital and the largest city in Colorado.
It has a metropolitan population of  over 2 million people, and covers over 4500 square miles. Denver was first home to the high plains Native Americans, including the Sioux, Cheyenne, Arapahoe and Apache. Now it is a city rich in ethnic backgrounds with a diverse cultural makeup.
<P>
<P>The top attractions include the Denver Museum of Natural History, Elitch Gardens, Denver Botanical Gardens, the Denver Mint, and Coors Brewing Co.
<P>

</center>
<font size=3>
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>
