<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->
<center>
<H1>BANKING PAGE</H1>
<H3>Monument, Colorado</H3>
<img border=0 width=350 height=200
<IMG SRC="./graphics/monucop1.jpg" ALT="[picture]" ALIGN=center><BR>

</center>

<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->


<P>Monument, Colorado is the hub community of the Tri-Lakes area in northern El Paso County.  Other communities in the area served by Monument resources are Palmer Lake, Woodmoor and Gleneagle.<p>
Monument is also just north of Colorado Springs, and it is bordered on the south by the U.S. Air Force Academy.  The most spectacular views are of the Front Range of the Rocky Mountains directly to the west of town.<p>
<P>The best full-resource for seniors currently available is through:
<font size=2>
<center>
          Pikes Peak Area Agency on Aging
<BR> Senior Information & Referral Service
<BR>                       15 South 7th Street
 <BR>                     Colorado Springs, CO 80905
<BR>                        Phone (719) 471-2096  Fax (719) 471-1226 
<font size=3>
</center>
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>
<P>From here visit Monument area Senior Banking Web Pages for: <p>
<a href="./webs/peobnk.htm">Peoples National Bank</a><br>
