<H1>HOUSING PAGE</H1>
<H3>Colorado Springs, Colorado</H3>
<img border=0 width=350 height=200
<IMG SRC="./graphics/cospp1.jpg" ALT="[picture]" ALIGN=center><BR>
<BR>
</center>
Nestled at the foot of Pikes Peak, Colorado Springs is the second largest city in Colorado.
It has a metropolitan population of just over 400,000 people, with approximately 75,000 of them being 50+.
<P>
<P>The number one attraction is the U. S. Air Force Academy and its famous Cadet Chapel. The number one photo op is The Garden of the Gods with Pikes Peak in the background.
<P>
<P>The best full-resource for seniors currently available is "The Yellow Book"; published by:<P>
