<center>
<H1>FINANCIAL PLANNING PAGE</H1>
<H3>Pueblo, Colorado</H3>
<img border=0 width=350 height=85
<IMG SRC="./graphics/pueblol2.gif" ALT="[picture]" ALIGN=center><BR>

</center>

<!-- Generation of PM publication page 1 -->


<P>Pueblo Colorado, the Steel city, has re-established itself as a prosperous Colorado community. It is located about an hour-and-a-half south of Denver, off I-25 and along the Arkansas River. A few years ago, Pueblo was voted one of the best places to live in the United States.
<p>
The number one attraction is the Pueblo Reservoir, where summer visitors can enjoy fishing, camping,  hiking, and swimming. The town is also the host of the Colorado State Fair, where each August since 1872 Coloradans have come to the fairgrounds.

<P>The best full-resource for seniors currently available is through:
<font size=2><p>
<center>
<b>       Pueblo Area Agency on Aging
<BR> Senior Information & Referral/Assistance </b>
<BR>                       1120 Court Street Suite 101
 <BR>                     Pueblo, CO 81003
<BR>                        Phone (719) 583-6611  Fax (719) 583-6323 
<font size=3>
</center>
<P>
<center>
<IMG SRC="./graphics/swash4.gif"><BR>
</center>
