<font size=7><b>
A <font size=5>Community of Choice...<br></b><font size=3>
<P>Village at Skyline is a community of 88 Apartments and 75 Garden Homes to lease,  and 61 Equity Homes nestled in the foothills of the Rocky Mountains in Colorado Springs, Colorado. Construction has begun on another apartment complex of 90 apartments to be completed in the fall of 1997. Village of Skyline's 6 year plan, which includes assisted living and skilled health care will bring total senior care to one scenic location.
<P>
<P>One of 82 Service Units of the National Benevolent Association, Christian 
Church (Disciples of Christ), Village at Skyline is keeping true to the motto: "What We Do 
Best Is Care". Village at Skyline is committed to providing more for residents than 
just housing. Village at Skyline offers a caring community where friends and 
neighbors make a special effort for each other, and where trained staff take a genuine interest in residents.<p>


