<HEAD>

<TITLE>Advertising Rates for Oregon Welcomes You!</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<a href="index.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/tico.gif" border=0 alt="Oregon Welcomes You!"></a>

<a href="member.htm"><img align=bottom src="gifs/member.gif" height=50 border=0 alt="back"></a>
<p>

<H1>Advertising on <I>Oregon Welcomes You!</I></H1>

<P>
<P>

<B>Why Advertise on <I>Oregon Welcomes You!</I>?</B>
<P>
<b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> reaches people around the world who are interested
in visiting Oregon.  The <i>Oregon Directory</i> has listings of visitor
industry related facilities, organizations, and events across
Oregon.  When you advertise on <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b>, you directly
target an affluent audience interested in visiting Oregon.  Communities
and regions can benefit from advertising on <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b>
because it will help them to &quot;stand out in the crowd&quot;-bringing
<b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> visitors directly to a community or region's
web page.  Advertising can also serve to highlight special events,
resorts, and attractions.
<P>
<B>Description</B>
<P>
There are two types of ads available on TICO's <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> web site: rotating and exclusive.
<P>
<B>Rotating Ads:</B>  
<P>
An ad shares placement with up to five other ads that are displayed
in rotation.  Each time that particular page is accessed a different
ad is displayed.  Users may click on the ad and be taken to the
advertiser's web page or another page of choice.
<P>
<B>Exclusive Ads:</B> 
<P>
One space on each page is reserved for an exclusive ad.  This
ad is displayed each time the page is accessed, and is not in
rotation with any other ads.  Users may click on the ad and be
taken to the advertiser's web page or another page of choice.
<P>
<B>Rates</B>
<HR>

<PRE>
<B>Monthly Advertising Rates for Oregon Welcomes You!                        

                              Rotating Ads               Exclusive Ads         

Ad Location</B>                 Member / Non-Member         Member / Non-Member 
  
<i>Oregon Welcomes You!</i>          $250 / $375                 $700 / $850      
<i>Home Page</i>                                                                   

<i>Oregon Directory</i>              $150 / $200                 $250 / $375      

<i>Visitor Information</i>           $100 / $135                 $200 / $300

<i>Lodging</i>                       $100 / $135                 $200 / $300      

<i>Dining</i>                        $100 / $135                 $200 / $300      

<i>Activities and</i>                $100 / $135                 $200 / $300    
<i>Events</i>                                                                       

<i>Recreation</i>                    $100 / $135                 $200 / $300     
 

</PRE>
<HR>

<P>
<B>Requirements</B>
<P>
All pages must be linked back to the <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b>
home page using the official logo.  Advertisers will be provided
with link guidelines and the logo when they advertise with TICO
for the first time.  Advertisers not wishing to carry the <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> 
logo on their page should add an additional 10%
to the standard advertising rates.
<P>

<hr>
<p>

<B>For information on ordering an ad on TICO's <b>Oregon Welcomes You!</b> web site, call 541-926-5604.   Or send us e-mail at <a href="mailto:sales@tico.org">sales@tico.org</B>
</BODY>

</HTML>








