<h2><center>The Oregon Welcomes You! Survey</center></h2>
1.  How did you find <strong>Oregon Welcomes You!</strong>
<SELECT NAME="1">

       <OPTION> Web surfing
       <OPTION> An article in the newspaper
       <OPTION> Visiting another Oregon tourism page
       <OPTION> The VIA campaign
       <OPTION> None of the above      
    </SELECT>

<p>If none of the above, please explain: <INPUT NAME="other_source" TYPE=text SIZE="30"<br>

<p>2.  Where are you from?<SELECT NAME="2">

       <OPTION> Oregon
       <OPTION> California
       <OPTION> Washington
       <OPTION> None of the above 
       </SELECT>
<p>If none of the above, please explain: <INPUT NAME="other_state" TYPE=text SIZE="30"<br>

