<INPUT NAME="eastern" TYPE=checkbox>   Eastern Oregon
<INPUT NAME="blank" TYPE=checkbox>   Other: <INPUT NAME="other_region" TYPE=text SIZE="20 " </pre>

<p>4.  What suggestions do you have for improving <strong>Oregon Welcomes You!</strong>?<br><TEXTAREA NAME="4" ROWS=10 COLS=60></TEXTAREA>

